[I] Computer-aided translation system

[T] Lokalize is the localization tool for KDE software and other free and open
[T] source software. It is also a general computer-aided translation system
[T] (CAT) with which you can translate OpenDocument files (*.odt).

[U] https://apps.kde.org/lokalize/

